data.description: Ok, folks!!! Here it is! It's finally on the market! It's everything you ever wanted!!!! Ready.... Well maintained 2,900 Square foot 3/2.5 bathroom home built in 2006 with office and bonus room, lots of storage, giant pantry, vaulted ceiling in the Master Bedroom, 10 Acres, Partial Ownership of Big Fishing Lake, Pool, Shop with Full Kitchen and Full Bathroom, Playset, HUGE garden, Fruit trees, Muscadine vines, Berries, RV/Camper Shed, Equipment Shed, Storm Shelter, Caledonia School District, tons of outdoor living areas (there are literally porches everywhere), wide open spaces, etc... All in a suburban area between Columbus and Caledonia.
